snippet.title: Geometry - 45-45-90 Triangles
snippet.description:
Math Bobby returns for a follow-up lesson on the famous 45-45-90 triangle. Geometry is no match for the guardian of knowledge, the triangular triumph, the right angle wrangler! We go through several examples, including references to the SAT. YAY MATH!
